    <item>
      <title>Oracle告诉客户第二次攻击，登录数据被盗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/oracle-tells-clients-of-second-recent-hack-log-in-data-stolen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两个熟悉此事的人说，Oracle Corp.告诉客户，黑客闯入了计算机系统并偷走了旧客户登录凭据。这是该软件公司在上个月向客户承认的第二次网络安全漏洞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/oracle-tells-clients-of-second-recent-hack-log-in-data-stolen</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
