    <item>
      <title>苹果生产枢纽受到关税的打击，使股票暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司（Apple Inc.）在总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的新关税中直接发现自己，即使经过一年的努力使iPhone制造商免受贸易战和供应链中断的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/apple-shares-slide-after-tariffs-threaten-to-hit-production-hubs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Neuralink在全球招募脑植入物研究</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/neuralink-recruits-globally-for-research-on-brain-implants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的大脑植入公司Neuralink正在寻找世界各地的患者，以参与该设备的研究，使人们可以利用自己的思想控制计算机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/neuralink-recruits-globally-for-research-on-brain-implants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 20:37:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
